/*  scroll-progress bar: a thin brand-coloured line that fills (scales along its
    x-axis) as the reader scrolls down the page. The scaling is driven by the
    shared scroll logic in Progress.astro, which must also be on the page.  */
---
<div
    id="scroll-progress"
    class="h-0.5 origin-left bg-accent"
    style="transform: scaleX(0)"
></div>
